Package com.gonzalo

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CorrectPackageVerifierTest
    Verifies if the method for creating random test data works correctly
    CreateService
    Servlet for creating random test data for its use in testing
    DoDeleteTest
    Test for DELETE requests.
    DoGetTest
    Test for GET requests.
    DoPostTest
    Test for POST requests.
    DoPutTest
    Test for PUT requests.
    Flight
    This class contains all data of a flight, including flight code, airport (arrival and departure) codes and date/time of arrival and departure
    GeoLocation
    Class for storing latitude and longitude of a location and do simple operations with them
    HolidayPackage
    This class represents the main entity used in the database, it stores both inbound and outbound flights, as well as the chosen hotel and the package price.
    HolidayPackagesServlet
    This class holds every response to petitions for HolidayPackages, implementing basic CRUD methods
    Hotel
    The class includes all data for a hotel, including its code, name, location and its star rating.
    IncorrectPackageVerifierTest
    Verifies if the method for verifying HolidayPackage entities works correctly
    MockHttpServletResponse
    This mock class is created to enable basic unit testing of the HolidayPackagesServlet class.
    ObjectifyWebFilter
    Filter required by Objectify to clean up any thread-local transaction contexts and pending asynchronous operations that remain at the end of a request.
